{"tid":2315294,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[代開Hea game]PES 2021 討論區 ( 6 )","createTime":"2020-12-07T06:03:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T04:00:13.000Z","uid":33456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a14c99947b99a26721b9324ef29641e00ebaa311","tid":2315294,"uid":33456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T06:03:11.000Z","msg":"希望大家貼下自己關於PES既GIF圖，一齊開心一齊笑鳩下隻GAME <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">首先為大家帶上萬眾期待既LEGEND，我近兩集都係用呢條友既</span><br />\n<br />\n教學短片︰<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B38awHf476U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DB38awHf476U&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTiZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=fadb496a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B38awHf476U</a><br />\n <br />\n <br />\n下載網址︰<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1vGdF4ZL-uXQZEmsglIw4JbrenyHU_txg/view\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1vGdF4ZL-uXQZEmsglIw4JbrenyHU_txg%2Fview&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTiZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=5a7dd822\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1vGdF4ZL-uXQZEmsglIw4JbrenyHU_txg/view</a><br />\n其他下載網址呢條片下面都有<br />\n<br />\n唔係英文唔緊要，簡單黎講就係將個文件入落手指，文件為WEPES，之後入GAME，去編輯果度，揀匯入球隊，然後全選就OK。<br />\n<br />\n入完之後去最底果兩隊明星隊度CHECK下有冇問題就得<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">如果主打單機同聯賽既朋友留意，係呢兩隊明星隊既任何球員都唔會係大師聯賽出現，所以如果你想玩LEGEND，必須將佢地手動轉會去其他球會。如果你唔鐘意有幾個版本既碧咸、細哨等等，你可以將佢地留番係明星隊，咁留係度果個就唔會出現。 <br />\n另外就係，如果你好鐘意某D球員，你想等佢地重生再升既，咁你要留意下佢本身體力夠唔夠，例如美斯係隻GAME大概得75體力，咁佢16歲重生果陣大概係55-60，基本上係好難用，我比較建議適量地加少少去到81-83會好D。<br />\n<br />\n如果你係馬勒當拿、托迪既FANS，咁你要諗下要唔要加番D體能啦，因為傳統十號位置呢個踢法本身個訓練對體能加得好少，而且重生果陣又會削好多體能，好似托迪咁，25歲得75體能，即係35歲果陣隨時得番57-63，可以估計到重生可能都係得55-62左右，如果佢成45歲先退既，咁隨時會更低，唔好以為PES做唔出呀，我就見過車斗里得49體能重生喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">每次官方既轉會更新後有可能LEGEND會消失，你重新導入就可以，唔會都係聯賽入面消失，但你更改過既外觀將會重設左</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">好啦，到球衣喇</span><br />\n<br />\n教學︰<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=794KlZUZzCs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D794KlZUZzCs&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTiZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=fbf6042d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=794KlZUZzCs</a><br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<br />\n都係相信道理啦，下載左落手指，之後去EDIT匯入就可以了<br />\n<br />\n下載網址︰<a href=\"http://www.mediafire.com/file/wgizwtqx6zyxmqu/PES_2021_Season_Update_Option_File_ps4.rar/file\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mediafire.com%2Ffile%2Fwgizwtqx6zyxmqu%2FPES_2021_Season_Update_Option_File_ps4.rar%2Ffile&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTiZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=27f7b21c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mediafire.com/file/wgizwtqx6zyxmqu/PES_2021_Season_Update_Option_File_ps4.rar/file</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2FF6TW2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2FF6TW2&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTiZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=e320db89\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2FF6TW2</a><br />\n<br />\n我冇驗證過得唔得，因為我冇買2021 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過一般都冇問題既<br />\n<br />\n希望大家玩得開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSkill move入電腦中路分享 : <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UBV4Zwo.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUBV4Zwo.gif&h=3adf7978&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uBxV6bz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuBxV6bz.gif&h=17d4fa30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fvKtGMY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfvKtGMY.gif&h=44ba70bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/evWvU7A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FevWvU7A.gif&h=802d7eda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n插花變向 (最好配備剪刀假動作技能)<br />\n<br />\nR2+右菇指向球員左或右，然後左菇推任何方向，但以右菇反方向效果最好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雙腳觸球( 最好配備雙腳觸球技能)<br />\n<br />\n右菇推向球員左或右，然後左菇推向任何方向(不可與右菇相同方向），但以左菇推前效果最好最快<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n漏波過人 : 只撳實R2 <br />\n<br />\n漏波俾隊友 : 只L1+R2 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n假動作練習建議大家去training試下個手感先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本POST新增小建議，如果你大舉進攻果緊回傳，後防又俾人MARK死哂，建議大家要善用L2既手動傳球，特別係進攻角球踢番去後半場果陣，可以用手動傳球俾D向後既直線/斜線波自己人追，好過傳到腳俾人截，對玩家對AI一樣有效 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望2022新引擎會有啲進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b3f2f4d65807dd2d92e49a8e5aa28debd1da03","tid":2315294,"uid":33456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T06:03:43.000Z","msg":"幾日都無人開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />隻驚沉得咁快咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ee9f050004af88ed742cf23ebbfc6040ee90c08","tid":2315294,"uid":33456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T06:05:00.000Z","msg":"最近幾日又送左一堆黑波傳奇比人抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61862919cd80d12cb1eba0b133850e7b65fb1398","tid":2315294,"uid":48391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T06:05:51.000Z","msg":"【PES 2021 討論區】(6) 1001咗無人講咪我講囉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2312223\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2312223</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br 